@startuml
' 让 PlantUML 按照自上而下的顺序布局
top to bottom direction
skinparam linetype ortho


database "Neo4j\n知识图谱"     as Neo4j
cloud    "DeepSeek R1\n大语言模型" as AI
rectangle "后端\n(FastAPI)"      as Backend

rectangle "前端\n(React + Vite)" as Frontend {
  [NeoGraph 可视化]   as NG
  [ChatPanel AI 问答] as CP
  [LearnPanel 学习记录] as LP
}

actor 学生 as Student

' —— 接口调用关系 —— 
Student  --> NG       : 浏览/点击节点  
Student  --> CP       : 输入问题  
Student  --> LP       : 标记已学  

NG       --> Backend  : GET  /api/graph-data  
CP       --> Backend  : POST /api/ai/generate  
LP       --> Backend  : POST /api/learning/mark  

Backend  --> Neo4j    : Cypher 查询/更新  
Backend  --> AI       : prompt + 已学概念  
AI       --> Backend  : 返回生成内容  

Backend  --> Frontend : JSON 响应

@enduml
